  {
    "@id": "https://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/ticketing/tap-water-jam-pre-party",
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "This pre-party kicks off the Tap Water Jam festival!The street dance community comes together on the floor through cyphers, exchange, and contagious energy. DJs take full control with a carte blanche, freely moving across sounds and influences in the spirit of hip hop and house culture.Two back-to-back sets will drive the night: Rafiki b2b Mab’ish, followed by Noey Lopez b2b Frankie J.A first night to reconnect, build energy, and set the tone for the weekend ahead."
      }
    ],
